- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a game-theoretic approach to semantics.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with the interpretation of programming language constructs.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with infinite processes and their complexity.
